Author: joojjoojjo
Text: Bulimia makes us do the strangest things and we just think it's normal, but it's so odd to everyone else! Your post just reminded me when you said about walking back in the room acting like you hadn't been fishing for beef in the toilet.  I've done a number of strange things in toilets over the years! Always thinking that people somehow know. But they never do.  Sending love to you!

Author: Little-Rexy
Text: Oh MY! (Dunno where to begin or go with this knowledge) I do have to admit although terribly sad in one aspect; you wrote in a fashion that made me kind of chuckle. Eating Disorders Suck! (hugs)
